Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.07,0:14:46.90,Dialogue,Yin,0000,0000,0000,,Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.51,0:14:48.36,Dialogue,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,Yin!
